All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
Main class for the game.
Army
Army is a holder for units to be later used in the battle class
ArmyEditorController
Army editor controller The Controller is responsible for adding modifcation ability to the army.
Battle
This class is used to simulate a battle between 2 armies
BattleMap
This is a class meant for keeping the different tiles in the game and allowing for units to move and "see" within the map.
CavalryUnit
CavalryUnit that is a type of unit.
CentralController
A class that main premise is to work as a communication and creation tool for the MainMenuController All code that creates a new instance of a scene are within this class for better readabilty as if they would be normally in the MainMenuController
CommanderUnit
This is the class for the CommanderUnit.
FileController
A controller meant to give the program read/write functonality to files It can export and read CSV as the documentation asked for
InfantryUnit
Infantry units, normal foot soldiers basically
LoadMenuController
Army Loads controller The Controller is responsible for fetching the information on what file to load and what army to load to.
MainMenuController
The main menu controller The controller that contains all the information needed
RangedUnit
A unit that focuses in ranged attacked.
Terrain
The different Terrains that will exist in the game
Tile
A tile on the map It will replace the terrain with BattleMap to allow for both terrain and units to be stored on the same key
Token
Token class The Token class is responsible for holding a unit and a color.
Unit
Base class for every Unit class.
